<note>B. This square is the entrance to the mine. Any player who enters
this room may take 5,000 gold coins. However, as long as he is
carrying the gold, he may not attack or defend himself. If the
Hero puts the gold down, it will disappear back into the mine.</note>
<note>The Quest is over when all of the monsters are killed or when all
of the Heroes have left the Quest by returning to the stairs on a
roll of 2 or 12. When the game is over, tell the players that all the
gold found at the mine entrance is fool’s gold and is worthless.
Any other treasure that is found is real.</note>
